1 SECTION 4. The Task Force established by Section 2 of this act may create a pilot
2 program for eligible active-duty Department of Defense certified Special Operations Forces
3 personnel in an effort to evaluate the overall implementation of any program recommended under
4 Section 2 of this act to exempt personal identifying information from the public record.
5 SECTION 5. Sections 2 and 3 of this act become effective January 1, 2027. The
6 remainder of this act is effective when it becomes law.".
